This is for the people that don’t use grams.

-Cake
5 egg yolks
1/4 cup of sugar 
Pinch of salt
1 tsp of vanilla extract
1/3 cup vegetable oil
1/2 cup of milk
2/3 cup cake flower
1/2 tsp of baking powder
-Meringue
5 egg whites
1/3 of cup of sugar 
-Filling
1/2 cup of heavy whipping cream
1/8 cup of condensed milk
